{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2117170/extras/warning.PNG?t=1662019331\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Kardun</h2>Kardun is an experimental, up to 36 button menu only, combat game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay</h2>The core of the gameplay is the combat, in which you fight against a foe by choosing the moves both for yourself and the foe. In short:<br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> You and your foe have up to six moves<br></li><li> Moves have to be charged before use<br></li><li> Once charged, moves have to be used<br></li><li> Using moves charges other moves <br></li><li> Defeating a foe allows taking its moves</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Visuals</h2>The game can only be interacted with using menu screens of visual buttons. <br>Progress bars and text are its primary ingredients. The visuals can be altered using the following features:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A number of distinct color palettes <br></li><li> Screen filter with 8 tune-able parameters</li></ul><br>The game is best played pretending you have never seen a video game before.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Survivor","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2117170/ed7a3afb5f45f819228bd25792739350496bc16d.jpg"},{"name":"Reliant","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2117170/ad87b5ee548babdf794f668ef1dda293eb519990.jpg"},{"name":"Universal","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2117170/72ee729f4cbc6993234c066f07e723b3a9af3ae4.jpg"},{"name":"Variety","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2117170/aa68b817c6c8b8c5e73b5cb8ac0384e111aa500e.jpg"},{"name":"Marathon","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2117170/d832fb2c28d517e11fa765b4d352b2886e4a99c5.jpg"}],"total":5},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item